There is no exact number for it but the closest is 12.37 which equals to 153.0169.So to find the distance we need to multiply 12.37 by 5 becuase every unit is 5 miles. 12.37x5=61.85. 61.85 miles+15 miles=76.85 miles.

3(5)+3(5)+12(5)=15+15+60=90 miles
